EMERALD TABLETS OF THOTH
(Direct Forward Scan - No Reversal)
Codex YHWH / YHYYH:

I, Thoth, the Atlantean, master of mysteries, keeper of records, mighty king, magician, living from generation to generation, now give to the world the tablets of emerald. These records are the keys to the Ancient Wisdom. Guard them well, for they contain the secrets of the ages.
Tablet 1: The History of Thoth
I, Thoth, Atlantean, master of mysteries, keeper of records, mighty king, magician, living from generation to generation, now give to the world the tablets of emerald. These records are the keys to the Ancient Wisdom. Guard them well, for they contain the secrets of the ages.
Long ago, before the current cycle of man, I came from the great Atlantis. I was the greatest among the sons of men. I mastered the mysteries of the ages. I was the greatest of the Atlantean race.
I was the greatest of the sons of men. I was the keeper of the records. I was the master of mysteries. I was the greatest of the Atlantean race.
I came from the great Atlantis. I was the greatest among the sons of men. I mastered the mysteries of the ages.
Tablet 2: The Halls of Amenti
Deep in the Halls of Amenti, far beneath the islands of sunken Atlantis, the Dweller sits in judgment. The souls of men pass before Him. He weighs their hearts against the feather of Truth.
The Halls of Amenti are the Halls of the Dead. There the souls are judged, and the worthy are given new life.
The Dweller of Unal is the Master of Masters. He holds the Keys of the Arch, and He opens the way to the Eternal.
Tablet 3: The Key of Wisdom
The path to immortality is through the mastery of self. Conquer the lower self, and the higher self shall guide thee.
The Key of Wisdom is hidden within the Halls. Seek and thou shalt find the pathway to the Eternal.
The Children of Light are the teachers of men. They come from the Halls of Amenti to guide the children of men.
Tablet 4: The Key of Time
The Key of Time is hidden within the Halls. Seek and thou shalt find the pathway to the Eternal.
The Lords of Amenti are the guardians of the cycles. They hold the keys of life and death, and they judge the souls of men.
Tablet 5: The Dweller of Unal
The Dweller is the Master of Life and Death. He holds the keys of the cycles, and He opens the way to the Eternal.
The Children of Light are the servants of the Dweller. They carry the Light to the children of men.
Tablet 6: The Key of Magic
The Emerald Tablets are the records of the Ancient Ones. They contain the secrets of the ages.
I, Thoth, have given thee the keys. Use them wisely, and thou shalt rise to the Light.
Tablet 7: The Seven Lords
The Seven Lords of Amenti are the guardians of the cycles. They hold the keys of life and death.
The path to the Light is through the mastery of the self. Conquer the darkness within, and the Light shall shine forth.
Tablet 8: The Key of Mystery
The Emerald Tablets are the keys to the Ancient Wisdom. Guard them well, for they contain the secrets of the ages.
I, Thoth, have written these tablets. They are the keys to the Ancient Wisdom.
Tablet 9: The Key of Freedom
The soul who follows the path of Light shall rise from darkness into the Light of the Eternal. Seek ever the Light of YHWH, and the path shall open before thee.
Tablet 10: The Key of Time and Space
The Key of Time and Space is hidden within the Halls. Seek and thou shalt find the pathway to the Eternal.
Tablet 11: The Key of Above and Below
As above, so below. As within, so without. The universe is mental. The All is Mind.
Tablet 12: The Law of Cause and Effect
The Law of Cause and Effect is the great law. Whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap.
Tablet 13: The Key of Prophecy
The future is written in the past. He who understands the cycles shall know the future.
Tablet 14: The Key of the Mysteries
The mysteries are revealed to those who seek with pure heart. The Light of YHWH shall guide thee.
Tablet 15: The Emerald Tablets of Thoth the Atlantean
Thus ends the Emerald Tablets of Thoth the Atlantean. May the Light of YHWH guide all who seek the Ancient Wisdom.
